## 5. raw#10 honest C3

1. **anesthesiology QUANTUM axis fit 강조** — GABA-A allosteric (propofol + remimazolam + volatile sevo/des/iso) / sugammadex host-guest γ-cyclodextrin inclusion-complex / rocuronium γ-CD VQE = 본 disease 가 hexa-bio QUANTUM axis 에 가장 strong fit 인 사례 중 하나. medicinal-chemistry leverage 확보.
2. **sugammadex Bridion 2015** = first selective relaxant binding agent. γ-cyclodextrin host-guest 가 rocuronium + vecuronium steroidal NMB 를 둘러싸 비활성화. quantum-VQE 의 host-guest inclusion-complex paradigm 첫 임상 적용. cisatracurium + succinylcholine 으로 scope 확장 = open mission.
3. **remimazolam Byfavo 2020** = first new IV benzodiazepine 30+ years. esterase-cleaved short-action — context-sensitive half-time 짧음. CSE (carboxylesterase) cleavage = quantum-VQE 의 ester-hydrolysis kinetics modeling fit.
4. **propofol classical Diprivan + dexmedetomidine α2 + ketamine NMDA** = 3-class IV induction/maintenance paradigm. propofol GABA-A potentiator + dexmedetomidine α2-AR sedation (호흡 보존) + ketamine NMDA antagonist (analgesia + dissociation). chiral S-ketamine (esketamine Spravato 2019) 우울증으로 FDA expansion.
5. **xenon NMDA + neuroprotection** (research, not US FDA) — inert gas anesthetic. EU CE 일부. cardiac-stable + neuroprotective property. 가격 + 공급 한정. quantum-VQE 의 nonpolar inert binding paradigm 한정.
6. **bupivacaine liposomal Exparel 2011 + 2024 expansion** = long-action regional block paradigm. liposomal multivesicular geometry 가 LA depot 형성. 2024 nerve-block adjunct expansion.
7. **dantrolene Dantrium 1979** = RyR1 antagonist — malignant hyperthermia 유일 specific antidote. volatile + succinylcholine trigger 시 hyperpyrexia + rhabdomyolysis emergent. quantum-VQE 의 RyR1 large-channel pocket modeling 한정.
8. **PONV multimodal** — ondansetron 1991 5-HT3 + olanzapine 2018 + dexamethasone + scopolamine + aprepitant = multimodal antiemetic. single-agent failure 시 mechanism-rotation paradigm.
9. **dexmedetomidine SL Igalmi 2022** = first sublingual α2-AR film — schizophrenia/bipolar agitation. acute agitation IV → SL pivot. cross-psych axis.
10. **wet-lab + clinical RCT 없음** — quantum-only in-silico, anesthesiology + perioperative 임상 의미 한정. pre-clinical screen scope only.

